BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:jZsH3lw8IXbRXYgqSN2i8
SUMMARY:Spacesuit Design Contest Workshop
DTSTAMP:20260325T052417Z
DTSTART:20260403T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Need help or inspiration with your design for the Spacesuit Des
	ign Contest? Join us for our NEW Free First Thursday drop-in workshops! Mu
	seum staff will lead workshops to help contestants learn about different i
	mportant parts of a spacesuit\, ask questions\, think through ideas and st
	art to figure how to build their own spacesuits.  About Spacesuit Design C
	ontest For this contest\, entrants must design and draw an original Spaces
	uit that follows the theme and all Contest requirements and rules. The top
	 entrants in each category will then build their design as a wearable\, bu
	t not functional\, spacesuit. The Top 5 Spacesuit designs in each category
	 will be showcased in a Fashion Show on Saturday\, June 27\, 2026. A panel
	 of judges will decide the winning design for each age category \\(four ca
	tegories total\\) and the four winning designs will be showcased at Fashio
	n in Flight in November 2026.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/det
	ails/spacesuit-design-contest-workshop/18260314/2026-04-02T00\n\nFrom SEAt
	oday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/spacesuit-design-contest-
	workshop/18260314/2026-04-02T00
